{"_id":"76iJI6FK2CVM6W99","name":"Spacer","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You live in space, you were born for it. No one can move with zero G like you do, and you can patch up anything with enough time and some tape. You're more valuable on ship than any fancy pilot.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: Mechanic's workshop, diagnostics kit, quality space suit, well lived in.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"FQT3S4d9qkOVHol5","name":"Merchant","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You've gone up in the world. No more hawking rubbish for you, you are a person of quality, a true trader, and people know it. You don't sell the things you trade, you talk about them. Others deal in the grubby business of selling.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: Fine clothes, a writ of trade from the Merchant Combine, a haulage vessel and suitable orbital warehouse.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}