{"_id":"I5FfqgHYcqT5rqxy","name":"Captain","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You command a ship, and others follow. Your piloting skills are legendary, and you know how to bark out commands. Others snap to order as you pass, which is how it should be. You've earned it.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: A starcraft and crew, a captain's uniform, a duelling blade and ornate gun.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"QcV2cqTJJ19jSBfy","name":"Gunslinger","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You're a killer. Not an assassin, but a fighter. When it comes to the crunch everyone wants you on their side. They might not like you, but they know that when things go south, the safest place is at your side.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: A quality, practical blade and high-quality gun. A hat and trench coat. A mean stare.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"ma