{"_id":"Zhf6DKU1hK2tVMst","name":"Doctor","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Unfortunately, the Chorus can be a dangerous place. Luckily, you and your comrades do your best to patch up the injured and heal the sick. Not that anyone thanks you, but you don't do it for the thanks. Luckily.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: Doctors diagnostics and medical kit, a datapad full of the latest medical research, some pills for when it all gets too much.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ff3QDqwiKHT2ISA3","name":"Agent","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>In the back-streets of the space port, in the passages of the Merchant Combine, or on some alien world, you know where to go and who to speak with to find out what you need. And if you need to obtain a certain rare and valuable piece of information for your masters, well that is easily done.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: Nondescript clothing, heavy cloak, poisoned weapon, implanted storage for datacubes.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"