{"_id":"jEA1keuAsO2Yzf0o","name":"Gang Boss","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Amongst criminals and killers, you're the boss. They listen to you, or at least they do as long as you find easy pickings for them. They'll be quick to turn on you if things don't go well. So make sure the money flows...</p>\n<p>Required equipment: A sturdy, well-made weapon, a vicious club of some kind, a gaggle of followers and a hideout somewhere in port.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"o8J7FDFO6389FiRO","name":"Warp Lord","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You've collected enough glyphs, and learnt enough of the warp, to call yourself a lord. Now others tremble at your power. As long as you don't make a mistake manifesting your glyphs, the Chorus is at your feet. Just don't make a mistake...</p>\n<p>Required equipment: At least five glyphs, impressive and esoteric robes, a staff inset with a jewelled eye to show others of your power.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"oEPbnxAFDt3S0Jnu","name":"Assassin","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You are a killer, nothing more, nothing less. A killer for money. What else is there to kill for? The Chorus has plenty of people that others want dead, for a myriad of reasons. You simply make sure that it happens, for jades. It's a living.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: A poison kit and blade, chameleon outfit, a disguise kit.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Warp focus":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Zero G":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"ZtfDqSvKTGtngaYG":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"qF83nX8w42wZn4uK","name":"Hunter","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The wild lands hold no fear for you. Travelling across the worlds of the Chorus, you have discovered creatures others would only dream of, and killed them. No one knows the wild worlds like you do.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: A finely crafted hunting rifle, a vicious blade, navigation equipment and a tent and camping gear.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"Animal handler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Astronav":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blades":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pilot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ship gunner":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small arms":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximum